# Dragon boat - low poly hull + improved head + tail (manual)
# +Z up, +X bow, +Y port
# v + f only (triangles)
# Groups: hull (inner/outer open-top shell with thickness band), head (upper/lower jaw, horns, crest, cheek fins), tail (S-curve stalk + single fin)
# Note: Preview for shape confirmation; not welded to hull; final ~6k version will merge and refine.

o dragon_boat_low_hull_head_tail_v2
s off

